{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·009.1", "text_original": "匏有苦葉，濟有深涉，深則厲，淺則揭。", "text_normalized": "匏有苦葉，濟有深涉，深則厲，淺則揭。", "notes": "匏有苦葉 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·009.2", "text_original": "有瀰濟盈，有鷕雉鳴，濟盈不濡軓，雉鳴求其牡。", "text_normalized": "有瀰濟盈，有鷕雉鳴，濟盈不濡軓，雉鳴求其牡。", "notes": "匏有苦葉 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-009__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·009.3", "text_original": "雝雝鳴鴈，旭日始旦，士如歸妻，迨冰未泮。", "text_normalized": "雝雝鳴鴈，旭日始旦，士如歸妻，迨冰未泮。", "notes": "匏有苦葉 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-009__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·009.4", "text_original": "招招舟子，人涉卬否，人涉卬否，卬須我友。", "text_normalized": "招招舟子，人涉卬否，人涉卬否，卬須我友。", "notes": "匏有苦葉 Chinese stanza 4."}
